🚀 Personal Portfolio Website
This is a  animated personal portfolio website built using HTML and CSS. It showcases your skills, projects, and contact form with a visually appealing design.



🎯 Features:-
✨ Animated background with smooth gradients
🧠 Skills section with cards
💼 Projects showcase with styled cards
📬 Contact form for user interaction
👣 Footer with profile and social media icons

🛠️ Technologies Used
-> HTML5
-> CSS3 (with Flexbox, Grid, Animations)
-> Google Fonts (Poppins)
